---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { installerScripts } from "../../lib/install";
---

<BaseLayout title="Install ankicli on Linux">
  <p class="eyebrow">Linux install</p>
  <h1>Install ankicli on Linux</h1>
  <pre><code>{`curl -fsSL ${installerScripts.shell} | sh`}</code></pre>
  <p>The installer downloads the Linux x64 standalone archive, verifies its checksum, and installs <code>ankicli</code> into <code>~/.local/bin</code>.</p>
  <pre><code>ankicli --version
ankicli --json doctor backend</code></pre>
</BaseLayout>
